TITLE: Loading a Preconfigured Highcharts Theme
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to include a preconfigured theme JavaScript file to style Highcharts visualizations. Themes apply styling options globally through the Highcharts.setOptions method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/highcharts/highcharts/blob/master/docs/getting-started/your-first-chart.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/themes/gray.js"></script>
```

