TITLE: Loading Highcharts Stock with Maps module
DESCRIPTION: Example of loading Highcharts Stock bundle and then adding Maps functionality as a module.
SOURCE: https://github.com/highcharts/highcharts/blob/master/docs/getting-started/install-from-npm.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Highstock bundle includes Stock and basic Highcharts
