TITLE: Implementing JSONP Request with Highcharts
DESCRIPTION: Client-side JavaScript code using jQuery to fetch JSONP data and initialize a Highcharts spline chart. Demonstrates how to configure chart options and populate series data from the JSONP response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/highcharts/highcharts/blob/master/docs/working-with-data/getting-data-across-domains-jsonp.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
$(document).ready(function() {
    var options = {
        chart: {
            renderTo: 'container',
            type: 'spline'
        },
        series: [{}]
    };

    var url =  "http://url-to-your-remote-server/jsonp.php?callback=?";
    $.getJSON(url,  function(data) {
        options.series[0].data = data;
        var chart = new Highcharts.Chart(options);
    });
});
```

