TITLE: Creating SVG Element with Attributes in JavaScript for Highcharts
DESCRIPTION: This function creates an SVG element with specified attributes. It uses the document.createElementNS method to create the element in the SVG namespace and sets the provided attributes using setAttribute.
SOURCE: https://github.com/highcharts/highcharts/blob/master/samples/highcharts/website/themes-demo/readme.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
function createElement(tag, attrs) {
    const element = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', tag);
    for (const key in attrs) {
        if (Object.hasOwnProperty.call(attrs, key)) {
            element.setAttribute(key, attrs[key]);
        }
    }
    return element;
}
```

